Did Justice Hwang

01:04:30.053 --> 01:04:32.973
also help you get a job at JB Daehan?

01:04:34.891 --> 01:04:37.060
Yes, my father said

01:04:38.019 --> 01:04:41.022
the written exam and the interview were
just for formality

01:04:42.273 --> 01:04:44.484
and that I'd get the job, no matter what.

01:05:07.841 --> 01:05:12.303
LETTER OF RESIGNATION

01:05:12.387 --> 01:05:15.390
The Judiciary is in a huge shock
once again.

01:05:15.473 --> 01:05:17.475
Justice Hwang, under the allegations

01:05:17.559 --> 01:05:20.145
of colluding with unfair hiring practices
and taking bribes

01:05:20.228 --> 01:05:21.938
submitted his letter of resignation.

01:05:22.397 --> 01:05:23.523
The prosecution explained

01:05:23.606 --> 01:05:26.109
Justice Hwang allegedly took bribes
from a construction company

01:05:26.192 --> 01:05:27.444
and used his networks

01:05:27.527 --> 01:05:29.654
to get his son a job he didn't qualify for

01:05:29.738 --> 01:05:32.824
and that they planned on summoning him
for questioning soon.

01:05:33.158 --> 01:05:36.036
Justice Hwang submitted
his letter of resignation this morning

01:05:36.119 --> 01:05:39.289
and left the court without a word.

01:05:42.667 --> 01:05:44.419
The prosecution is aware

01:05:44.544 --> 01:05:46.046
of Justice Hwang receiving bribes

01:05:46.129 --> 01:05:49.632
and his involvement
in unfair hiring practices.

01:05:49.716 --> 01:05:52.552
They will announce
a date for his questioning soon.

01:05:52.635 --> 01:05:54.471
Chief Justice Jeon Heung-woo is

01:05:54.554 --> 01:05:56.806
also taking responsibility by resigning

01:05:56.890 --> 01:06:00.351
for the damaged reputation
of the Judiciary.

01:06:00.643 --> 01:06:02.896
The Office of the President has made

01:06:02.979 --> 01:06:04.898
an official nomination of Baek Yi-seok

01:06:04.981 --> 01:06:06.566
as the next Chief Justice.

01:06:06.649 --> 01:06:08.985
Power changes are happening rapidly
within the Judiciary

01:06:09.069 --> 01:06:11.571
and the employees within the court
are wondering

01:06:11.654 --> 01:06:14.240
if this will signal a reformation

01:06:14.324 --> 01:06:15.992
of the whole system.

01:06:18.203 --> 01:06:21.498
I'll invite you to the room
with the best views once you retire.

01:06:22.916 --> 01:06:23.917
Here.

01:06:41.810 --> 01:06:43.978
Your son will have to pay
for what he's done.

01:06:45.063 --> 01:06:46.064
But I'll let you get away

01:06:46.147 --> 01:06:48.608
with non-custodial investigation
and probation.

01:06:51.736 --> 01:06:53.321
But of course

01:06:54.989 --> 01:06:57.325
you'd better not let Suojae hear
about our deal.

01:07:21.724 --> 01:07:23.143
What a pathetic man.

01:07:24.352 --> 01:07:26.604
He got bitten in the ass by his own son.

01:07:31.734 --> 01:07:33.361
Here we are.

01:07:45.456 --> 01:07:46.958
Don't trust anyone here.

01:07:47.876 --> 01:07:50.086
And don't speak
unless you're asked a question.

01:07:50.628 --> 01:07:52.964
Don't be surprised
by anything you see or hear.

01:07:55.758 --> 01:07:56.801
You'll look stupid.

01:07:57.844 --> 01:07:58.887
Yes, sir.

01:08:07.604 --> 01:08:09.189
Is today

01:08:09.856 --> 01:08:12.317
the day we fill our treasure chest?

01:08:13.109 --> 01:08:14.611
Yes, sir.

01:08:15.361 --> 01:08:16.487
Mr. Han

01:08:18.323 --> 01:08:21.492
you know why I'm still going so strong
to this day?

01:08:21.951 --> 01:08:23.328
I don't know, sir.

01:08:23.703 --> 01:08:25.371
Because the world is the same.

01:08:26.623 --> 01:08:30.043
It never changes, does it?

01:08:43.806 --> 01:08:44.807
Introduce yourself.

01:08:47.018 --> 01:08:49.187
I'm Judge Lee Han-young
at the Seoul Central Court.

01:08:50.813 --> 01:08:53.650
I'm here
to serve the nation and our people.

01:09:08.456 --> 01:09:09.499
Take a seat.

01:09:41.239 --> 01:09:42.824
This is a special activity fund
from the National Intelligence Service.

01:09:58.006 --> 01:09:59.632
This is from the prosecution.

01:10:12.312 --> 01:10:14.063
This is
from the Ministry of National Defense.

01:10:24.490 --> 01:10:26.284
This is from the National Police Agency.

01:10:38.588 --> 01:10:39.714
Alright, then.

01:10:40.673 --> 01:10:42.050
Let's serve our nation.

01:11:08.868 --> 01:11:10.244
These crazy bastards!

01:11:13.414 --> 01:11:17.418
THE JUDGE RETURNS

01:11:41.567 --> 01:11:42.985
The elimination has begun.

01:11:43.069 --> 01:11:44.195
They have a record
of everywhere we've been

01:11:44.278 --> 01:11:45.613
and our call history!

01:11:45.696 --> 01:11:47.323
Sin-jin is going to catch on soon.

01:11:47.407 --> 01:11:49.409
I'll get rid of Gwang-to,
who relies on mere shamans

01:11:49.492 --> 01:11:51.119
and become the leader of Suojae.

01:11:51.202 --> 01:11:52.662
So, who is that?

01:11:52.745 --> 01:11:53.955
Judge Lee Han-young.

01:11:54.038 --> 01:11:55.706
And Sin-jin is behind it?

01:11:55.915 --> 01:11:58.626
The prosecution will indict him
while in custody

01:11:58.709 --> 01:12:01.712
and Judge Lee, whom we met at the Suojae,
will be on the case.

01:12:02.046 --> 01:12:03.881
Hey, Byeon. Let's save a life.

01:12:03.965 --> 01:12:05.258
Sin-jin and Gwang-to.

01:12:05.341 --> 01:12:06.634
I must stop both of them

01:12:06.717 --> 01:12:09.137
or the country's justice will be gone
for good.

01:12:13.349 --> 01:12:15.351
Subtitles by: Min-sun Kim